Get parameters

Source: R/getter.R
waGetPara.Rd

Get parameters

waGetPara(name = NULL)

Arguments

name

Variable name which will return. All parameters will return if NULL

Examples

library(weaana)
data("records") 
waGetPara( "yrange" )
